'''赛仕软件'''（SAS Institue Inc.），是一家在[[美国|美国]]成立的跨国[[软件|软件]]研发公司。主要产品为商业统计分析软件系统[[統計分析系統|SAS]]。赛仕软件是全球最大的私营软件企业<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/22/business/22sas.html?pagewanted=all|title=Rivals Take Aim at the Software Company SAS|last=Lohr|first=Steve|accessdate=2018-11-21|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214134527/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/22/business/22sas.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是被[[财富500强|财富500强]]企业使用最多的软件供应商<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://archive.fortune.com/2010/01/21/technology/sas_best_companies.fortune/index.htm|title=SAS is the Best Company to Work For - Jan. 21, 2010|accessdate=2018-11-21|last=contributor|first=By David A. Kaplan,|work=archive.fortune.com|archive-date=2014-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829180237/http://archive.fortune.com/2010/01/21/technology/sas_best_companies.fortune/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

赛仕在中国大陆由负责市场营销的“赛仕中国”和负责研发的“赛仕软件研究开发北京有限公司”组成。

